description:
Supplementary files for Jennifer Erin Gleason&#39;s PhD thesis. 

 &nbsp; 

  Appendix 1 &ndash;  A word document elaborating on data cleaning protocols post-bioinformatic processing using metabaR. 

  Appendix 2  &ndash; The R code used to clean the data following the protocol in Appendix 1. 

  Appendix 3  &ndash; Raw data post JAMP processing, to be used in the code from Appendix 2. Composed of 4 csv files (Read table, OTU taxonomy data, PCR metadata, sample metadata). 

 &nbsp;

